data.description: Absolutely Gorgeous!!! Come and see this Beautiful Ranch Style Home with a fully finished Basement! 5 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, 2 Family Rooms and a 2 Car Attached Garage. Lot's of space for a growing family or to entertain. Beautifully maintained hardwood floors on the main Level, New Paint throughout the interior and the exterior, New Furnace and New AC, New wooden Deck up front and much more! The Kitchen is open and inviting with a large Island and Stainless Steel Appliances! The Washer and Dryer are included along with a 2nd Refrigerator. The Family Room is right of the kitchen, has beautiful wooden beams, a Fireplace for those cozy evenings with the family and french doors to the back yard as well as direct access in to the private court yard! There are three bedrooms on the main floor including the Master Bedroom as well as two additional bedrooms in the basement. The basement has a huge Rec Room, a Bathroom and a very large storage area that can serve as an additional non confirming bedroom if needed. Lots and lots of room for the square footage! If you enjoy outdoor space there is a private court yard, a large concrete patio and a big fenced in back yard! Tastefully decorated throughout, this house feels like home from the moment you walk in! Come and see this Beauty Today!
